ovement over the previous year's collection.  The civic body's efforts in tracing vacant land tax owners and taking lawful actions contributed to this revenue growth. The target for the upcoming financial year is set at 90% collection.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/vijayawada-municipal-corporation-achieves-267-crore-tax-collection-in-fy26/129970934?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-54700/129970934.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}]}